'''塞巴斯蒂安·福斯-索勒沃格'''（{{lang-no|Sebastian Foss-Solevåg}}，{{bd|1991年|7月13日||}}）生于奥勒松，是一名挪威男子高山滑雪运动员<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.voelkl.com/en/athletes/sebastian-foss-solevaag/|title=SEBASTIAN FOSS SOLEVÅG|work={{lang|de|Völkl}}|accessdate=2021-03-07|archiveurl=https://archive.is/KmSwF|archivedate=2021-03-07}}</ref>。他在两岁时便开始接触[[滑雪|滑雪]]，当时他的两个姐姐已经在参与滑雪运动，而他家人的其中两个朋友都是高山滑雪国家队成员<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.pyeongchang2018.com/en/game-time/results/OWG2018/en/alpine-skiing/athlete-profile-n3025436-sebastian-foss-solevaag.htm|title=Athlete Profile: Sebastian FOSS-SOLEVAAG|work=Pyeongchang 2018|accessdate=2021-03-07|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180420010013/https://www.pyeongchang2018.com/en/game-time/results/OWG2018/en/alpine-skiing/athlete-profile-n3025436-sebastian-foss-solevaag.htm|archivedate=2018-04-20}}</ref>。2012年，他在[[芬兰|芬兰]]莱维完成了个人的世界杯分站赛首秀<ref>{{cite web|url=https://skiracing.com/sebastian-foss-solevaag-wants-to-be-more-than-a-slalom-skier/|title=Sebastian Foss-Solevaag Wants to Be More Than a Slalom Skier|work=Ski Racing|date=2019-08-26|accessdate=2021-03-07|archiveurl=https://archive.is/SXmKn|archivedate=2021-03-07}}</ref>。

